These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-1::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: surfing, snowboarding, swimming, soccer
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, bolivar, siglo, oliveros
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, colombian, indonesian, polish
The people use 4 different means of transport: bus, jet-ski, tram, trike
1. the colombian is the oliveros-smoker##1
2. the indonesian is between the person who's sport is swimming and the person who's sport is soccer##2
3. the colombian is the person driving the bus##1
4. the person driving the trike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
5. the vegafina-smoker is on the left of the canadian##1
6. the person driving the tram is the person who's sport is swimming##1
7. the bolivar-smoker is on the left of the person who's sport is soccer##1
8. the canadian is on the far right##1
9. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2     |     3      |    4     |
| Sport   | snowboarding | soccer   | surfing  | swimming  |
| Cigar   | bolivar    | oliveros    | vegafina      | siglo    |
| Nationality   | polish | colombian | indonesian | canadian |
| Transport     | trike  | bus       | jet-ski    | tram     |

