.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-2::.
The people use 4 different means of transport: scooter, motorbike, helicopter, train
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, adventure, scientific, western
4 different pets are kept: bird, dog, frog, lizard
There are 4 different favourite colors: azure, coral, green, grey
1. the person who likes grey is on the right of the person driving the train##1
2. the person driving the scooter is on the far right##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the person who likes coral##1
4. the person driving the helicopter is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
5. the person watching western movies is between the owner of the frog and the person who likes azure##2
6. the person who likes grey is between the person watching western movies and the owner of the lizard##2
7. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
8. the person watching adventure movies is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
9. the person watching scientific movies is on the right of the owner of the dog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Transport         | train | motorbike    | helicopter  | scooter    |
| Movie-Genre   | action      | adventure  | western  | scientific |
| Pet           | lizard      | frog       | dog      | bird       |
| Color         | coral    | grey | green | azure |

