.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-3::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: blend, bluemaster, oliveros, davidoff
City: san-francisco, colone, hannover, liverpool
The people have 4 different jobs:  analyst, lawyer, paramedic, pilot
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, motorbike, roller, subway
1. the paramedic is the person driving the motorbike##1
2. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the pilot##1
3. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the motorbike##1
4. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the helicopter##1
5. the oliveros-smoker is on the left of the person traveling to hannover##1
6. the lawyer is the person traveling to liverpool##1
7. the davidoff-smoker is on the right of the person traveling to hannover##1
8. the blend-smoker is between the person traveling to san-francisco and the person traveling to liverpool##2
9. the person traveling to hannover is between the oliveros-smoker and the lawyer##2

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1     |     2     |      3      |     4     |
| Cigar        | bluemaster | oliveros     | blend   | davidoff     |
| City       | colone   | san-francisco   | hannover | liverpool |
| Job         | analyst   | paramedic | pilot       | lawyer    |
| Transport   | roller    | motorbike | helicopter  | subway    |

