.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-2-4::.
There 4 different types of food: strawberry, pepper, papaya, artichoke
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: action, disaster, martial-arts, scientific
There are 4 different favourite colors: ivory, emerald, yellow, aquamarine
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: ice-hockey, rugby, soccer, volleyball
 1. the person watching disaster movies is on the far right##1
 2. the person watching scientific movies is the person eating strawberry##1
 3. the person who likes ivory is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
 4. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the far left##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is the person who likes emerald##1
 6. the person who likes aquamarine is on the right of the person who's sport is ice-hockey##1
 7. the person watching disaster movies is the person eating papaya##1
 8. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 9. the person eating strawberry is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
10. the person eating pepper is between the person who likes ivory and the person eating artichoke##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3       |       4        |
| Food           | strawberry  | artichoke | pepper     | papaya |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | action  | martial-arts | disaster       |
| Color           | emerald       | aquamarine    | yellow      | ivory           |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | rugby   | volleyball   | soccer         |

