 4. the security-guard is on the left of the person driving the car##1
 5. the person watching scientific movies is on the left of the russian##1
 6. the australian is on the left of the person watching scientific movies##1
 7. the social-worker is on the left of the polish##1
 8. the lawyer is the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the australian is between the person driving the jet-ski and the person watching adventure movies##2
10. the person watching romance movies is the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |       2       |       3       |     4      |
| Nationality          | thai         | australian         | polish     | russian      |
| Job           | security-guard | social-worker | freelancer    | lawyer     |
