 6. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
 7. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to paris##1
 8. the fan of house is on the far right##1
 9. the person traveling to edinburgh is between the person traveling to nizza and the person who's sport is cycling##2
10. the owner of the turtle is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |     3      |     4     |
