 7. the owner of the rat is on the left of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
 8. the owner of the turtle is between the dannemann-smoker and the old-henry-smoker##2
 9. the blend-smoker is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
10. the person who's birthday is in march is between the dannemann-smoker and the old-henry-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1      |     2      |      3      |       4       |
